---
---

<section class="services-section">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="section-title" data-mos="fade-down">
      導入事例
    </h2>
    
    <!-- 導入事例画像 -->
    <div class="title-image-container" data-mos="fade-up">
      <img src="/other/image13.png" alt="導入事例" />
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <!-- PRC Service -->
      <div class="service-card" data-mos="fade-up">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <h3 class="service-title">Photonics Reservoir Computingの社会実装</h3>
          <div class="service-content">
            <p>
              東京科学大学の研究室と連携し、世界最先端技術である
              Photonics Reservoir Computingの半導体の社会実装を研究している。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- DX Service -->
      <div class="service-card" data-mos="fade-up">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <h3 class="service-title">AI技術を用いたDX支援</h3>
          <div class="service-content">
            <p>
              企業独自の課題に合わせたオーダーメイドソリューションの提供により
              業務の効率化、販売促進を進める。<br/>
              実務経験豊富な最先端技術を研究しているメンバーが開発。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--services-bg, linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(240, 244, 248, 1) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 100%));
  }

  :global(.dark) .services-section {
    --services-bg: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 1) 0%, rgba(30, 41, 59, 1) 100%);
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 80px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .title-image-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .title-image-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--img-shadow, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
  }

  :global(.dark) .title-image-container img {
    --img-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .service-card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--card-bg, #f3f4f6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 2px solid var(--card-border, #d1d5db);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--card-shadow, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08));
  }

  :global(.dark) .service-card {
    --card-bg: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
    --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    --card-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 
      0 20px 40px var(--hover-shadow, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15)),
      0 0 60px var(--hover-glow, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.1));
  }

  :global(.dark) .service-card:hover {
    --hover-shadow: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
    --hover-glow: rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.15);
  }

  .service-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1.4;
    word-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .service-content {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-color, #334155);
  }

  :global(.dark) .service-content {
    --text-color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .service-content p {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .service-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .service-content {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
